## Legend

| Notation | Meaning |
|----------|---------|
| `actor` lane | Human role |
| `participant` lane | Bounded context or external system |
| `->>` | Synchronous call (request/response) |
| `-->>` | Synchronous reply |
| `--)` | Asynchronous emit (event, fire-and-forget) |
| `Note over A,B:` | Cross-lane note (invariant, compensating action) |
| Numbered steps | Auto-generated step IDs; cite in commits/ADRs |

